@startuml
title Fortuna - Registration and Login Flow

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend / Bruno" as Client
participant "CustomersController" as Controller
participant "RegisterCustomerCommandHandler" as RegisterHandler
participant "CustomerRepository" as CustomerRepo
participant "ProductRepository" as ProductRepo
participant "PasswordHasher" as Hasher
participant "UnitOfWork / WriteDbContext" as Uow
participant "LoginCustomerCommandHandler" as LoginHandler
participant "TokenProvider (JWT)" as TokenProvider

== Registration ==
User -> Client : Fill registration form
Client -> Controller : POST /api/customers
Controller -> RegisterHandler : RegisterCustomerCommand
RegisterHandler -> CustomerRepo : GetByEmailAsync(email)
CustomerRepo --> RegisterHandler : existing customer / null
RegisterHandler -> Hasher : Hash(password)
Hasher --> RegisterHandler : passwordHash
RegisterHandler -> CustomerRepo : AddAsync(customer)
RegisterHandler -> ProductRepo : GetNextNumberSequenceAsync()
ProductRepo --> RegisterHandler : next sequence
RegisterHandler -> RegisterHandler : Create default products\n(account + debit card [+ credit card])
loop for each default product
  RegisterHandler -> ProductRepo : AddAsync(product)
end
RegisterHandler -> Uow : SaveChangesAsync()
Uow --> RegisterHandler : customerId
RegisterHandler --> Controller : customerId
Controller --> Client : 201 Created

== Login ==
User -> Client : Submit email and password
Client -> Controller : POST /api/customers/login
Controller -> LoginHandler : LoginCustomerCommand
LoginHandler -> CustomerRepo : GetByEmailAsync(email)
CustomerRepo --> LoginHandler : customer
LoginHandler -> Hasher : Verify(password, hash)
Hasher --> LoginHandler : true / false
LoginHandler -> TokenProvider : Create(customerId, email)
TokenProvider --> LoginHandler : JWT token
LoginHandler --> Controller : AuthenticationToken
Controller --> Client : 200 OK (token, expiresAtUtc)

@enduml
